bluefish (1.0.7-3) unstable; urgency=low

  This package update provides fixed/improved/updated pattern for C, Python,
  PHP, Shell and XML. Pattern for D and Kid were added.

  Further several filetype pattern have been updated (e.g. for C files).

  To update your pattern, follow the instructions in README.Debian.

 -- Daniel Leidert (dale) <daniel.leidert@wgdd.de>  Wed, 26 Sep 2007 21:42:59 +0200

bluefish (1.0.5-1) unstable; urgency=high

  The package provides updates for several highlighting pattern (e.g. C,
  ChangeLog, CSS, SQL, Perl and PHP). To update your highlighting pattern,
  follow the instructions in README.Debian. There you will also find
  instructions for how to update custom menu files (the French localisation
  was updated and a few bugs were fixed).

 -- Daniel Leidert (dale) <daniel.leidert@wgdd.de>  Sat,  4 Feb 2006 22:39:12 +0100

bluefish (1.0.4-2) unstable; urgency=low

  The package updates highlighting patterns and custom menu files to fix
  several issues and bugs. See README.Debian for instructions, how to update
  highlighting pattern and custom menu files.

 -- Daniel Leidert (dale) <daniel.leidert@wgdd.de>  Mon, 16 Jan 2006 23:16:27 +0100

